title: Holiday With My Busty Cousin
description: After ten years, cousins Ken and Tomo—now with matured bodies—reunite during the holidays. They hit it off and commit the forbidden act, but little do they realize that it was observed by Ken's devilish little sister and the lengths that she'll go to prevent their love from blooming further...
author: Ichinomiya Yuu
